# Feature: sage doctor — 11/11 health bar.
Output ../assets/demo-doctor.gif
Output build/demo-doctor.txt
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Hide
Type "export PATH=$HOME/bin:$PATH NO_COLOR=1" Enter
Type "unset FORCE_COLOR 2>/dev/null" Enter
Type 'cd "$HOME/src/atlas" && clear' Enter
Show
Type "sage doctor"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
